\begin_layout Section

Assumptions and dependencies:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	In order for this system to function properly we will have to make a few
 assumptions about the users on the system.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	Firstly we are assuming that every user has a smartphone or tablet capable
 of running this system readily available to them.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	We are also assuming that they will access to internet on a constant connection.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	We have also assumened that they are IT literate and thus able to make
 use of the system.
 This assumption is however
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	neccesary in order to make this system.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	We are assuming that all users will remain connected to the system once
 on campus grounds for the detection of the 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	traffic density calculations.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	This system will rely on several aspects being functional.
 It relies on the Wi-Fi routers being spread across campus
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	grounds; that every user remains connected once on campus; that the hardware
 needed to run the system is in fact capable
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	of doing so.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	This system also relies on users having adaquete devices capable of running
 the system.
 Another depencies is that the users
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	input their interests so that relevant events are shown to them.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	The final assumption that we are making is that all university events as
 well as the university calendar is up to date so as to 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph

	correctly display only current events of the day.
\end_layout

